-RiverMist-Resorts-1024x1024.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/rivermistresorts.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/Malnad-cuisine-special-Filter-Coffee-at-RiverMist-Resorts-300x300.jpg 300w, https:\/\/rivermistresorts.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/Malnad-cuisine-special-Filter-Coffee-at-RiverMist-Resorts-150x150.jpg 150w, https:\/\/rivermistresorts.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/Malnad-cuisine-special-Filter-Coffee-at-RiverMist-Resorts-768x768.jpg 768w, https:\/\/rivermistresorts.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/Malnad-cuisine-special-Filter-Coffee-at-RiverMist-Resorts.jpg 1080w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" \/>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-2db7a4c elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"2db7a4c\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https:\/\/www.instagram.com\/coffee__and_conversations\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Image Credit: Dorathy Agnes<\/a><\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-8d61f14 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"8d61f14\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>The Malnad region of Karnataka is located on the western and eastern slopes of the Western Ghats and is famous for its coffee plantations. The Malnad coffee has a legendary reputation for being one of the best filter coffees South India has to offer. There is a unique way behind this filter coffee making and that\u2019s what makes it special.<\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-c248aa9 elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"c248aa9\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t<h2 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">Pathrode<\/h2>\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-4e1d1ba elementor-widget elementor-widget-image\" data-id=\"4e1d1ba\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"image.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/rivermistresorts.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/elementor\/thumbs\/Malnad-cuisine-typical-Pathrode-at-RiverMist-Resorts-polwn93dbdewvjhwbj7iz4iwtezr70qa3yhjhqg2m8.jpg\" title=\"Malnad cuisine typical Pathrode at RiverMist Resorts\" alt=\"One of the most popular and typical Malnad food is Pathrode\" loading=\"lazy\" \/>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-84cf68e elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"84cf68e\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https:\/\/www.instagram.com\/nayaksumanth\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Image Credit: <span class=\"_7UhW9    vy6Bb       qyrsm KV-D4            se6yk       T0kll \">Sumanth Nayak<\/span><\/a><\/p><p>One of the most popular and typical Malnad food is Pathrode. It is also known by the name Patravadi and consists of key ingredients like colocasia leaves commonly known among the locals as pathrode leaves, rice, coconut paste, tamarind, and spices.<\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-2f810fd elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"2f810fd\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t<h2 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">Jackfruit dishes<\/h2>\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-b16ba04 elementor-widget elementor-widget-image\" data-id=\"b16ba04\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"image.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img decoding=\"async\" width=\"1024\" height=\"1024\" src=\"https:\/\/rivermistresorts.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/Malnad-cuisine-special-Jackfruit-dishes-at-RiverMist-Resorts-1024x1024.jpg\" class=\"attachment-large size-large wp-image-5135\" alt=\"Jackfruit Idli is one of the main jackfruit dishes in Malnad food\" srcset=\"https:\/\/rivermistresorts.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/Malnad-cuisine-special-Jackfruit-dishes-at-RiverMist-Resorts-1024x1024.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/rivermistresorts.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/Malnad-cuisine-special-Jackfruit-dishes-at-RiverMist-Resorts-300x300.jpg 300w, https:\/\/rivermistresorts.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/Malnad-cuisine-special-Jackfruit-dishes-at-RiverMist-Resorts-150x150.jpg 150w, https:\/\/rivermistresorts.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/Malnad-cuisine-special-Jackfruit-dishes-at-RiverMist-Resorts-768x768.jpg 768w, https:\/\/rivermistresorts.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/Malnad-cuisine-special-Jackfruit-dishes-at-RiverMist-Resorts.jpg 1080w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" \/>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-2f4c1ee elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"2f4c1ee\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https:\/\/www.instagram.com\/thesecretgobbler\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Image Credit: thesecretgobbler<\/a><\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-d3a0d26 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"d3a0d26\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>A variety of jackfruit-based dishes is one of the specialties of Malnad food. Snacks like Halasina Hannina Kadubu or Jackfruit Idli and Kayi Kadubu are the most popular among them. Both are the steamed version of sweets and have influenced the creation of several varieties of similar snacks across the state.<\/p><p>Halasina Hannina Mulka or Jackfruit Fitters and Halasina Kayi Pappad or Jackfruit Papad are 2 other famous jackfruit-based Malnad foods. The jackfruit dishes vary from sweet and savory as there are plenty of recipes used regularly. There are a lot of jackfruit dessert recipes available too.<\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-e446072 elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"e446072\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t<h2 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">Akki Rotti<\/h2>\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-bac536e elementor-widget elementor-widget-image\" data-id=\"bac536e\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"image.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/rivermistresorts.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/elementor\/thumbs\/Malnad-cuisine-popular-Akki-Rotti-at-RiverMist-Resorts-polwo7vec8r39pfo0ix6khkz6iojdpjj684c9xjh9k.jpg\" title=\"Malnad cuisine popular Akki Rotti at RiverMist Resorts\" alt=\"Akki Rotti is one of the most popular foods in Karnataka State\" loading=\"lazy\" \/>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-f53ba11 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"f53ba11\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https:\/\/www.instagram.com\/treat_teal\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Image Credit: <span class=\"_7UhW9    vy6Bb       qyrsm KV-D4            se6yk       T0kll \">Anvitha Hebse<\/span><br \/><\/a><\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-225da0f elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"225da0f\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>Akki Rotti is one of the most popular foods in Karnataka State. Even though the recipe varies from one region to another, this particular Malnad Akki Roti is the most common and favorite food among travelers here. The main ingredients of Akki Rotti look almost similar to that of neer dosa. The texture and the diverse taste are what distinguish them apart.<\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-146e272 elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"146e272\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t<h2 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">Hesarubele Carrot Kosambari<\/h2>\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-694bdf4 elementor-widget elementor-widget-image\" data-id=\"694bdf4\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"image.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/rivermistresorts.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/elementor\/thumbs\/Malnad-cuisine-important-Hesarubele-Carrot-Kosambariat-RiverMist-Resorts-polwoh9s8l3yht20hmzg9f7l4de7iokujin72p5jjc.jpg\" title=\"Malnad cuisine important Hesarubele Carrot Kosambariat RiverMist Resorts\" alt=\"Malnad cuisines important dish is Hesarubele Carrot also known as Mung dal carrot salad\" loading=\"lazy\" \/>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-90c3081 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"90c3081\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https:\/\/www.instagram.com\/swatis_fooddiary\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Image Credit: Swati Keshri , Food Blogger<br \/><\/a><\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-f7304a9 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"f7304a9\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>Another important Malnad dish is Hesarubele carrot Kosambari also known as Mung dal carrot salad. The simplicity of the dish is what makes it so special. Soaked raw green gram dal or mung dal and grated carrot are the main ingredients used in the preparation of this salad.<\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-f5f9bef elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"f5f9bef\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t<h2 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">Huli Avalakki<\/h2>\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-03f8b5c elementor-widget elementor-widget-image\" data-id=\"03f8b5c\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"image.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img decoding=\"async\" width=\"1024\" height=\"768\" src=\"https:\/\/rivermistresorts.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/Malnad-cuisine-tasty-Huli-Avalakki-in-RiverMist-Resorts-1024x768.jpg\" class=\"attachment-large size-large wp-image-5138\" alt=\"Malnad style Huli Avalakki is a tasty breakfast dish popular among the locals in Karnataka\" srcset=\"https:\/\/rivermistresorts.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/Malnad-cuisine-tasty-Huli-Avalakki-in-RiverMist-Resorts-1024x768.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/rivermistresorts.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/Malnad-cuisine-tasty-Huli-Avalakki-in-RiverMist-Resorts-300x225.jpg 300w, https:\/\/rivermistresorts.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/Malnad-cuisine-tasty-Huli-Avalakki-in-RiverMist-Resorts-768x576.jpg 768w, https:\/\/rivermistresorts.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/Malnad-cuisine-tasty-Huli-Avalakki-in-RiverMist-Resorts.jpg 1080w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" \/>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-a0a1d8f elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"a0a1d8f\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https:\/\/www.instagram.com\/nithyas_kitchen\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Image Credit: By Nithya Suneel<br \/><\/a><\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-3b45e30 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"3b45e30\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>Malnad style Huli Avalakki or Gojjavalakki is a tasty savory breakfast dish popular among the locals. Prepared by boiling salt, jaggery, and tamarind and then mixed with roasted red chili, gram dal, and urad dal powder, it is said to induce a sensory explosion in your taste buds. The Huli Avalakki recipe has a lot of different variations.<\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-64838d6 elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"64838d6\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t<h2 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">Cheenikayi Kadubu<\/h2>\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-af0d313 elementor-widget elementor-widget-image\" data-id=\"af0d313\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"image.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1024\" height=\"1024\" src=\"https:\/\/rivermistresorts.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/Malnad-cuisine-tasty-Cheenikayi-Kadubu-in-RiverMist-Resorts-1024x1024.jpg\" class=\"attachment-large size-large wp-image-5139\" alt=\"One of the specialty Malnad dishes is Cheenikayi Kadubu also called Pumpkin Idli\" srcset=\"https:\/\/rivermistresorts.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/Malnad-cuisine-tasty-Cheenikayi-Kadubu-in-RiverMist-Resorts-1024x1024.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/rivermistresorts.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/Malnad-cuisine-tasty-Cheenikayi-Kadubu-in-RiverMist-Resorts-300x300.jpg 300w, https:\/\/rivermistresorts.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/Malnad-cuisine-tasty-Cheenikayi-Kadubu-in-RiverMist-Resorts-150x150.jpg 150w, https:\/\/rivermistresorts.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/Malnad-cuisine-tasty-Cheenikayi-Kadubu-in-RiverMist-Resorts-768x768.jpg 768w, https:\/\/rivermistresorts.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/Malnad-cuisine-tasty-Cheenikayi-Kadubu-in-RiverMist-Resorts.jpg 1080w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" \/>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\